#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.265"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.265:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.265:0.2"
msgid "27. Kammapathavagga"
msgstr "27. Ways of Performing Deeds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.265:0.3"
msgid "265. Adinnādāyīsutta"
msgstr "265. Stealing"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.265:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with four qualities is cast down to hell."

msgctxt "an4.265:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.265:1.3"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca adinnādāyī hoti, parañca adinnādāne samādapeti, adinnādāne ca "
"samanuñño hoti, adinnādānassa ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—"
msgstr "They themselves steal …"

msgctxt "an4.265:1.4"
msgid "imehi kho … pe …."
msgstr "Someone with four qualities is raised up to heaven. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.254"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.265:2.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, parañca adinnādānā veramaṇiyā "
"samādapeti, adinnādānā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti, adinnādānā veramaṇiyā "
"ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—imehi kho, bhikkhave … pe …."
msgstr "They don’t themselves steal …"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.265:2.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
